casebody.data:
KATZ et al., Appellants, v. ATFIELD, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County,

General Term.

May 5, 1893.) Appeal, from city court, general term. Action by Bernard Katz and another against Catharine Atfield, administrs^trix etc

Argued before BOOKSTAVER, BISCHOFF, and PRYOR, JJ.

H. Daily, Jr., for appellants. John McGinn, for respondent.

No opinion. Appeal dismissed, with costs. See 20 N. Y. Supp. 892.
